Recruitment Consultant - Award Winning Employer
03 May 2014 05:51 PM - UAE
Job Description:
If you're a money driven individual looking to become a success in one of the most thriving industry sectors you should consider a career in a specialist IT Recruitment company. With a quick career plan that can take you to Director Level within a short space of time and the potential to earn between 30k and 40k OTE in your first year and potentially 100,000+ within 3 years it is a fantastic way to enter the corporate world.
I am looking for talented individuals to work for Computer Futures (part of Sthree Group) who are one of the largest and most successful recruitment companies in the UK and worldwide with over 8 offices in the UK and over 20 internationally (Inc New York / Tokyo / Paris / Dubai / San Francisco / Germany etc). Due to our success we are looking to bring through an additional 4 people to the team which is currently one of the most successful throughout the business. The role of a trainee recruitment consultant involves: * Building up a client base & building a market * Meeting with clients, establishing strong relationships * B2B Sales * Developing relationships with niche candidates, and helping them find an ideal job * Negotiation * Closing deals * Generating new leads and business opportunities The ideal candidate for a trainee recruitment consultant is or has * An excellent work ethic
* Strong communication skills * Entrepreneurial spirit * Sales experience * Very positive attitude * Desire to earn lots of money! Ideally we are looking for people with some sales experience (either B2B / B2C / recruitment / telesales / door to door sales) - this can be anything from 6months to 6years - we are looking for people at different levels. There are great benefits on offer from the start, including: - A VERY competitive basic salary - Uncapped commission structure - Car allowance / target - Holiday targets - Clear career progression within the business from trainee all the way up to director level - Training from one the best recruitment businesses in the country - this is a comprehensive training programme If you are interested in finding our more about the role, call one of the team - Tom Smith, Chris Reilly & Heather O'Rourke for a quick chat on [Telephone number removed] or send your CV by clicking 'APPLY NOW' and we will call yo (more...)
